entry.summary:
题目: 33. Search in Rotated Sorted Array
一个很清晰简洁的解法: Clever idea making it simple
int search(vector<int>& nums, int target) {
    int lo = 0, hi = nums.size();
    while (lo < hi) {
        int mid = (lo + hi) / 2;

        double num = (nums[mid] < nums[0]) == (target < nums[0])
                   ? nums[mid]
                   : target < nums[0] ? -INFINITY : INFINITY;

        if (num < target)
            lo = mid + 1;
        else if (num > target)
            // 这儿为什么不能 -1 ?
            hi = mid;
        else
            return mid;
    }
    return -1;
}

这个解法省了我几万个脑细胞, lo = mid + 1 很好理解, 但是 hi = mid - 1 为什么出错, 我想破脑袋都没想明白...

